<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Password Reset - Xeno Shopify Insights</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .otp-container {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Xeno Shopify Insights account. Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to proceed:</p>
    
    <div class="otp-container">
      <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
      <p>This code will expire in {{expiresIn}} minutes.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team if you have any concerns.</p>
    
    <p>Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@xeno.com">support@xeno.com</a>.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Xeno Shopify Insights. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // Add current year to the footer
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const yearElements = document.querySelectorAll('.current-year');
      const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
      yearElements.forEach(el => {
        el.textContent = currentYear;
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
